NAME
    PPI ( Parse::Perl::Isolated ) - Parsing an manipulating Perl code

DESCRIPTION
    Most of this is really broken, and put in CPAN for the benefit of the
    interested.

    The API is going to compltely change, the Lexer replaced. After that, we
    get docs.

    For now, look at the syntax highlighter in the samples directory.

